profitable businesses wwwcdrinccom   clayton dubilier  rice llc all rights reserved federal capital partners  what we do who we are what we do news contact investor login multifamily commercial structured investments portfolio fcp serves sustainability what we do federal capital partners® acquires operates and develops residential and commercial assets in the eastern us markets in addition we deploy capital in residential and commercial product sectors through joint venture equity mezzanine debt and preferred equity investments the array of transactions we have closed highlights our breadth and flexibility our focus on the eastern us gives us extensive local knowledge and valuable community relationships that local emphasis along with disciplined underwriting and a depth of experience developing operating and managing assets allows us to mitigate risks and adjust to change quickly fcp has offices in chevy chase md raleighdurham nc and south florida   fund managementfcp manages over  billion of capital and is currently investing its third fund a commingled discretionary fund closed in   our fund investments are targeted to multifamily office retail industrial manufactured housing and selfstorage assets in the eastern us  fcp funds are deployed in a variety of structures including equity preferred equity and mezzanine debt  wisconsin avenue suite   chevy chase md    federal capital partners  lacy i rice who we are what we do news contact investor login managing partners   alex marshall esko i korhonen thomas a carr lacy i rice acquisitions  investments finance  accounting asset management  construction administration partners lacy i rice managing partner lacy rice manages the company’s forsale and forrent residential acquisitions mr rice has  years of experience in real estate investment and corporate finance and serves on fcps investment committee prior to founding fcp mr rice was a principal at the carlyle group he served on the company’s real estate funds investmen